body:
Responding with half of an answer because if you are like me, you are playing on the weekend and want this to work.  I will try to do a PR tomorrow but I am virtually sure the issues starts here:

`inception/image_processing.py", line 397, in parse_example_proto bbox = tf.concat(0, [ymin, xmin, ymax, xmax])`

Concat changed in TF 1.0, the 0 goes at the end.  But there is more, tf.image_summary also changed.  I suggest running the tf [migration script](https://www.tensorflow.org/install/migration) on the file.  I believe the other files have been updated.
